SELECT transactions.* FROM transactions JOIN transactions_master ON `transaction-master-id` = transactions_master.id WHERE transactions_master.id = '10' AND `user_id` = '493' AND `posted-date` BETWEEN '2022-06-01' AND '2022-06-30'

SELECT transactions.sku, repo FROM transactions LEFT JOIN (SELECT reports.sku as repo FROM reports WHERE client_id = '493') as r ON transactions.sku = r.repo WHERE `transaction-master-id` = '10' AND transactions.sku IS NOT NULL AND repo IS NULL GROUP BY transactions.sku

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT transactions.* FROM transactions JOIN transactions_master ON `transaction-master-id` = transactions_master.id WHERE transactions_master.id = '10' AND `user_id` = '493' AND `posted-date` BETWEEN '2022-06-01' AND '2022-06-30'

timelineData.name: Query
timelineData.query: SELECT transactions.sku, repo FROM transactions LEFT JOIN (SELECT reports.sku as repo FROM reports WHERE client_id = '493') as r ON transactions.sku = r.repo WHERE `transaction-master-id` = '10' AND transactions.sku IS NOT NULL AND repo IS NULL GROUP BY transactions.sku
